Key Match Events: Georgia scored four goals with Khvicha Kvaratskhelia, Giorgi Chakvetadze, Georges Mikautadze, and Giorgi Kochorashvili; Lukas Kalvach scored Czechia's sole goal.
Others: The match was held at Mikheil Meskhi Stadioni in Tbilisi with a crowd of 20,401; referee Orel Grinfeld officiated the game.
